cs.CR, cs.HC, cs.GT, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of deception in cyber security, which falls under the category of "cs.CR" (Cryptography and Security). The paper also mentions the use of human-computer interaction and gamification, which suggests that it could also fall under "cs.HC" (Human-Computer Interaction) and "cs.GT" (Computer Science and Game Theory). The use of analytics and the analysis of interactive deceptive aspects suggest that it could also fall under "cs.SI" (Social and Information Networks) and "cs.CY" (Computers and Society).
